        "description": "Add a new visit log to a specific workflow step.\n\n**Authentication:** Required\n\n**Path Parameter:**\n- stepId (long): The ID of the workflow step\n\n**Request Body:**\n- visitDate (string, required): Format YYYY-MM-DD\n- timeIn (string, required): Format HH:MM:SS\n- timeOut (string, optional): Format HH:MM:SS\n- description (string, optional): Visit details\n- loggedById (long, optional): ID of the user logging the visit. Defaults to the authenticated user if omitted.\n\n**Business Logic:**\n- Validates that the step belongs to the user's company\n- Validates that timeOut is not before timeIn\n- Calculates workedMinutes automatically\n- Logs an activity record (VISIT_LOGGED) in the timeline\n\n**Response:**\n- id (long): Visit log ID\n- visitDate (string): Visit date\n- timeIn (string): Time in\n- timeOut (string): Time out\n- workedMinutes (long): Total minutes worked\n- description (string): Description\n- loggedById (long): ID of the user who logged it\n- createdAt (datetime): Creation timestamp\n- updatedAt (datetime): Last update timestamp"
